{"tid":2104663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區諾軒緊急呼籲：投票紙張供不應求， 有手機既用返電子投票 留返紙張俾有需要人士","createTime":"2020-07-12T06:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T08:32:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc967f7ef1dba28a457916adb0ad69fdb7a65d2","tid":2104663,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:33:36.000Z","msg":"一些很卑微的呼籲：<br />\n<br />\n由於大家投票真係好踴躍，紙張投票開始不敷應用， 雖然暫時仲頂得住，但係都呼籲大家可以用電子投票，就用電子投票，留返紙張比有需要嘅市民。我哋預計過咗今日紙張投票隨時有20,000票。<br />\n<br />\n我都好明白大家拉票好緊張，唔同團隊對於其他團隊宣傳品擺放有意見好正常，只係，大家都係民主派，希望大家用互諒互讓解決，管制始終係下一步嘅措施，而我哋都真係唔係政府，處理有限，我哋會盡力做，可以嘅話大家唔好擺咁多宣傳咁近票站啦，但大家互諒互讓，可以幫到我哋更多了😅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/581689778588087/posts/3036341579789549/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F581689778588087%2Fposts%2F3036341579789549%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=2aa59d81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/581689778588087/posts/3036341579789549/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"3fa96788f2d8fe2a9259eece6b3f79fa1ba09322","tid":2104663,"uid":36157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"其實電子好方便<br />\n宣傳少所以好多人唔知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利：電子投"},{"pid":"8c39cd6f6aef1d7d552a9e5d3895385cd92f4ed5","tid":2104663,"uid":53612,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:37:57.000Z","msg":"教年長投電子"},{"pid":"ffe8060ed1d68df1bac7c14d4f6ad7765fad2038","tid":2104663,"uid":245033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T06:39:22.000Z","msg":"電子投票真係好易<br />\n琴日排隊見到<br />\n唔洗教好耐<br />\n長輩都好快就識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e26b683eff2ff17ae8cd938d9dbacce45310952","tid":2104663,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.